page.title: 10KIRSTY'S DAY
page.content: A typical day in the life of Kirsty I get up in the morning about 8.30 .I get dressed and wake my mum up .I go down stairs and have some cornflakes .Then I go to school .When the teachers come we line up and go into the classroom .We do English then Top Ten then we go .When we go back in we do sums until lunch .I have banana rolls and a cup of coffee and then go back to school.We do gymn and then we have"free time",then it is play time. In free time I normally make junk models.The bell goes at 3.20 pm.I go home and get changed into my tennis things. I play with my friend Martin who is quite good but I normally beat him.Then I go in and have tea and do my homework and watch telly until 9.30 and then I get changed and wash myself and get into bed I read for a little while and then I go to sleep.
